feat: Improve Arabic translations, and implement region flags

## Features

### Akamaar Hire Message

- Added professional, non-pushy call-to-action in footer
- Implemented "Built by akamaar" messaging with dual contact options (website + email)
- Bilingual support (English/Arabic) for hire message
- Subtle design matching existing footer aesthetic

### Region Flags and Icons

- Created RegionFlag component for visual region identification
- Integrated SVG flag files for US, EU, Egypt, and Saudi Arabia
- Added Africa continent SVG icon
- Replaced generic Lucide icons with flags in region cards and title section
- Used Globe icon for global region

### Refresh Button Enhancement

- Added spinning animation during refresh operation
- Implemented proper async flow with error handling
- Added debouncing to prevent multiple simultaneous refreshes
- Improved visual feedback with disabled state and opacity
- Fixed refresh functionality to actually trigger data collection and reload

## Improvements

### Arabic Translation Overhaul

- Fixed region names: "عالمي" → "العالم" (Global), simplified country names
- Improved terminology: "التوجهات" → "المعنويات" (Sentiment)
- Updated sentiment labels: "إيجابي/سلبي" → "متفائل/متشائم" (Optimistic/Pessimistic)
- Refined app title: "مرصد الاتجاهات" → "مرصد الاقتصاد"
- Enhanced professional terminology throughout (e.g., "تحليل آلي" → "تحليل تلقائي")
- Improved footer disclaimer to be more professional
- Removed unnecessary punctuation and improved phrasing

